A Prince Falls For A Skater | A Royal Christmas on Ice | Holiday Romance

A prince travels to the United States to launch a new business venture, only to find himself captivated by a former Olympic figure skater. As they navigate the challenges of blending royal duties with everyday life, sparks fly both on and off the ice. Between glamorous events, unexpected obstacles, and the magic of the holiday season, their worlds collide, leading to a heartwarming romance filled with charm, laughter, and Christmas spirit.

2022.  Stars: Anna Marie Dobbins, Jonathan Stoddard, William Baldwin
